text: Aleksandr Soldatenkov (, born 1887, date of death unknown) was a Russian fencer. He competed in the individual and team épée events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1887 births Category:Year of death missing Category:Russian male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Russia Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics
